title: Avoid Emotional racing - love what you’re doing.
description:
Today’s podcast covers a rage of things I’ll focus on in the last 7 days before a marathon.

How the result won’t break my spirit or love for what I’m doing.

But make no mistake, I only see one outcome being possible. “Logically speaking”

Support the show
